<!-- ── ABOUT ME SECTION ── -->
<div class="home-about">
    <div class="home-about-inner">

        <div class="home-about-text">
            <p class="section-label">About Me</p>
            <h2>Exploring how technology<br>and business work together.</h2>
            <div class="home-about-divider"></div>
            <p>
                I'm Carlos Palomares, a student at Western Washington University studying
                Business Administration with a concentration in Management Information Systems,
                and I expect to graduate in Spring 2026.
            </p>
            <p>
                My interest in this field grew from a long-standing fascination with technology
                and how it can be used to improve the way people work and solve real problems.
                I became especially drawn to how technology and business systems come together
                to make processes more efficient and support better decision making.
            </p>
            <p>
                Beyond my academic interests, I enjoy traveling, photography, and spending time
                outdoors — experiences that push me to stay curious and continue growing through
                new perspectives.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="home-about-sidebar">
            <div class="home-about-facts">
                <div class="fact-item">
                    <span class="fact-label">Major</span>
                    <span class="fact-value">Business Administration (MIS)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="fact-item">
                    <span class="fact-label">Graduation</span>
                    <span class="fact-value">Spring 2026</span>
                </div>
                <div class="fact-item">
                    <span class="fact-label">University</span>
                    <span class="fact-value">Western Washington University</span>
                </div>
                <div class="fact-item">
                    <span class="fact-label">Hobbies</span>
                    <span class="fact-value">Travel &amp; Photography</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="home-about-social">
